PrecisAmendments to the UNEMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS (section 60) which will allow the Canada Employment and Immigration Commission to write-off various kinds of penalties or debts which occur through no fault of the U.I. claimant, such as overpayments, retroactive rulings, etcetera.
